.SH "Function Documentation"
.PP 
.SS "SDL_Surface* sgLoadPngMemory (const void * mem, Uint32 size)"
.PP
Load a PNG image from memory. 
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fImem\fP Memory area containing the PNG image 
.br
\fIsize\fP Size of the specified memory area
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
An SDL_Surface on success, NULL on error
.RE
.PP

.SS "SDL_Surface* sgLoadPngFile (const char * file)"
.PP
Load a PNG image from a file. 
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIfile\fP Path to the PNG file
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
An SDL_Surface on success, NULL on error
.RE
.PP

.SS "SDL_Surface* sgLoadPngFp (FILE * fp, int autoclose)"
.PP
Load a PNG image from a stdio file pointer. 
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIfp\fP FILE pointer, opened for reading 
.br
\fIautoclose\fP close the file after the operation when this is non-zero
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
An SDL_Surface on success, NULL on error
.RE
.PP

.SS "SDL_Surface* sgLoadPngRWops (SDL_RWops * rwops)"
.PP
Loads png from RWops into SDL_Surface. 
.PP
sgLoadPngRWops is stolen from SDL_image which is Copyright (C) by Sam Lantinga, Philippe Lavoie
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIrwops\fP The data source
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
An SDL_Surface on success, NULL on error
.RE
.PP

.SS "int sgSavePngMemory (SDL_Surface * surface, void * mem, Uint32 size)"
.PP
Save a surface as PNG image to memory. 
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIsurface\fP surface to save as .png 
.br
\fImem\fP destination buffer 
.br
\fIsize\fP max size of the buffer
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
0 on success, non-zero otherwise
.RE
.PP

.SS "int sgSavePngFile (SDL_Surface * surface, const char * file)"
.PP
Save a surface to a PNG file. 
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIsurface\fP surface to save as .png 
.br
\fIfile\fP path of the file to create
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
0 on success, non-zero otherwise
.RE
.PP

.SS "int sgSavePngFp (SDL_Surface * surface, FILE * fp, int autoclose)"
.PP
Save a surface to a stdio file pointer. 
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIsurface\fP surface to save as .png 
.br
\fIfp\fP path of the file to create 
.br
\fIautoclose\fP close the file after the operation when this is non-zero
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
0 on success, non-zero otherwise
.RE
.PP

.SS "int sgSavePngRWops (SDL_Surface * surface, SDL_RWops * rwops)"
.PP
Saves png from SDL_Surface into RWops. 
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIsurface\fP Surface to save as .png 
.br
\fIrwops\fP SDL_rwops we'll write to
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
0 on success, non-zero otherwise
.RE
.PP

